short_summary: Elder Services to provide Indigenous programs and services
description: The Canada Correctional Service is looking for an individual to provide Elder services to Indigenous offenders. It is the responsibility of the selected individual to create a welcoming environment that addresses the unique needs of Indigenous offenders.
